WEBVTT

00:00:01.105 --> 00:00:02.356 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hello.

00:00:02.356 --> 00:00:04.483 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m happy to invite you to a special event

00:00:04.483 --> 00:00:07.528 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that will be attended by millions of people.

00:00:07.528 --> 00:00:10.030 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s the anniversary of Jesus’ death.

00:00:11.115 --> 00:00:14.159 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This invitation shows
the time and location of the event

00:00:14.159 --> 00:00:16.161 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in our area.

00:00:16.161 --> 00:00:18.998 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We also invite you
to a special talk the weekend before.

00:00:19.540 --> 00:00:21.125 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thanks.

00:00:21.125 --> 00:00:22.543 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hmm.

00:00:22.543 --> 00:00:24.169 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The meetings are free?

00:00:24.628 --> 00:00:25.838 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes.

00:00:25.838 --> 00:00:27.882 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May I show you
this minute-and-a-half video

00:00:27.882 --> 00:00:30.175 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that explains
the significance of this meeting?

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:31.844 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sure.

00:00:33.387 --> 00:00:37.850 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagine a world filled with peace,

00:00:38.851 --> 00:00:41.186 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
free of suffering,

00:00:42.271 --> 00:00:44.982 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
an abundance of food for all,

00:00:46.066 --> 00:00:49.486 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and life in perfect health.

00:00:52.156 --> 00:00:55.784 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But how can this beautiful future
be possible?

00:00:57.620 --> 00:01:00.122 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of what Jesus did for us.

00:01:02.041 --> 00:01:05.002 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He came to earth for a purpose.

00:01:06.795 --> 00:01:10.674 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He gave his life for those he loved.

00:01:13.135 --> 00:01:15.137 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The night before he died,

00:01:15.137 --> 00:01:18.682 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jesus asked
that we commemorate his sacrifice.

00:01:20.684 --> 00:01:22.102 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He said:

00:01:22.102 --> 00:01:25.606 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Keep doing this in remembrance of me.”

00:01:27.358 --> 00:01:30.402 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On the anniversary of his death,

00:01:30.402 --> 00:01:33.822 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
people around the world
will gather to remember him.

00:01:34.657 --> 00:01:37.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses
invite you and your family

00:01:37.868 --> 00:01:41.246 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to attend the Memorial of Jesus’ death.

00:01:41.246 --> 00:01:43.624 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At that meeting, you will find out

00:01:43.624 --> 00:01:47.252 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
why his sacrifice was so important

00:01:47.252 --> 00:01:50.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how his promises affect you.

00:01:51.298 --> 00:01:53.842 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To find a location near you,

00:01:53.842 --> 00:01:58.055 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
please accept an invitation
from one of Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:01:58.055 --> 00:02:01.684 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or fill in the congregation
meeting search form

00:02:01.684 --> 00:02:04.103 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on jw.org.

00:02:04.895 --> 00:02:07.022 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I hope you can come.

00:02:07.022 --> 00:02:08.399 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thanks.

00:02:08.399 --> 00:02:10.526 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I need to check with my family,

00:02:10.526 --> 00:02:12.695 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but maybe you’ll see me there.

00:02:12.695 --> 00:02:14.196 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My name is Ed.

00:02:14.196 --> 00:02:15.531 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m Pete.

00:02:15.531 --> 00:02:17.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Perhaps the next time we talk,

00:02:17.157 --> 00:02:20.494 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can show you what the Bible says
about why Jesus died.

00:02:20.494 --> 00:02:22.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Is this normally a good time for you?

